dct_description_sm: Great Britain. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section.G.S.G.S. 4922. Great Britain. Directorate of Military Survey. War Office and Air Ministry. Alternate title: Series K 8413: Sheet: Kirkuk & environs. "Edition 1 -G.S.G.S. In upper right margin: "Refer to this map as Series K8413: Kirkuk & Environs." In upper left margin: "Kirkuk and District." This edition was "recompiled from MDR. MISC. 6790 and miscellaneous information up to 1955." Relief shown by hachures Oil wells, lines, and facilities are shown.
